    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it just feels like i'm a ghost. like i'm just going through the motions of a life that doesn't belong to me anymore. every day is just more of the same... waking up, eating, sleeping, all for a future that literally doesn't exist. it feels so futile. like i'm just waiting for something that's never coming back.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
